# Incremental Save + Rate Limit Recovery

- [x] Incremental save — save results after each successful segment
- [x] Rate limit popup — when all endpoints fail:
  - [x] Retry → auto-enable disabled endpoints → resume
  - [x] If all ON → ask to add new endpoint
  - [x] If no → save & stop
- [x] Wire callback from api_client through process_controller to UI
